name: WINDOWS APPLE [Maçã na Janela]
description: Glitch work done back in 2013 using (PS) Video Editing, (Blender) Modeling & Datamosh (HEX, Avidemux, etc) mixed techniques; this experiment was used on my Graduation Project at UNESP about Glitch and Creative Process in Design 'glitch, o meio do erro'.
